#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Systemsettings"
msgstr "Sistemske nastavitve"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "automount"
msgstr "samodejni priklop"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "device"
msgstr "naprava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows you to configure automatic mounting of disks and volumes."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko nastavite samodejno nameščanje diskov in zvezkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable the automatic mounting features in this module, you will not "
"need to use the device notifier applet or the navigation panel in the file "
"manager to get access to a recently plugged in device."
msgstr ""
"Če v tem modulu omogočite funkcije samodejne namestitve, vam za dostop do "
"nedavno priključene naprave ne bo treba uporabljati programa za obveščanje o "
"napravah ali navigacijske plošče v upravitelju datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top of the dialog you find the global settings, which can be "
"overridden for each single device in the <guilabel>Device Overrides</"
"guilabel> list. For a single-user desktop it is recommended to have all the "
"check boxes above the overrides list enabled."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu pogovornega okna so na voljo globalne nastavitve, ki jih lahko "
"prevladate za vsako posamezno napravo na seznamu <guilabel>Preglasitve "
"naprav</guilabel>. Za namizje z enim uporabnikom je priporočljivo, da so "
"omogočena vsa potrditvena polja nad seznamom prevlad."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable automatic mounting of removable media"
msgstr "Omogoči samodejno nameščanje izmenljivih medijev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is unchecked, no device automounting of any kind will happen, "
"regardless of anything selected in the <guilabel>Device Overrides</guilabel> "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Če ta možnost ni označena, ne bo prišlo do samodejnega nameščanja naprav, ne "
"glede na vse, kar je izbrano v razdelku <guilabel>Preglasitve naprav</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only automatically mount removable media that has been manually mounted "
"before"
msgstr ""
"Samodejno namesti samo odstranljive medije, ki so bili pred tem ročno "
"nameščeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is checked, &plasma; will only automatically mount devices it "
"remembers. A device is <quote>remembered</quote> if it has ever been mounted "
"before; &eg; plugging in a &USB; media player to charge is not sufficient to "
"<quote>remember</quote> it. If the files are not accessed, &plasma; will not "
"automatically mount the player next time it is seen. Once they have been "
"accessed, however, &plasma; will remember to automatically make the contents "
"accessible to your system."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost odobrjena, bo program &plasma; samodejno namestil samo "
"naprave, ki si jih zapomni. Naprava je <quote>zapomnjena</quote>, če je bila "
"že kdaj prej nameščena; &eg; priključitev &USB; medijskega predvajalnika za "
"polnjenje ne zadostuje za <quote>zapomnjenje</quote>. Če do datotek ni "
"dostopa, &plasma; ob naslednjem prikazu predvajalnika ne bo samodejno "
"namestil predvajalnika. Ko do njih dostopate, bo program &plasma; samodejno "
"omogočil dostop do vsebine v vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically mount all removable media at login"
msgstr "Samodejno namesti vse izmenljive medije ob prijavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If any removable storage devices are connected to your system when you login "
"to your desktop, &plasma; will automatically make the contents available to "
"your system for other programs to read."
msgstr ""
"Če so ob prijavi v namizje v sistem priključene odstranljive pomnilniške "
"naprave, bo &plasma; samodejno dala vsebino na voljo sistemu, da jo lahko "
"berejo drugi programi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically mount removable media when attached"
msgstr "Samodejno namesti izmenljive medije, ko so priključeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is checked, &plasma; will automatically make the contents of any "
"storage device available to the system when it is plugged in or attached."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &plasma; samodejno dala na voljo vsebino "
"katere koli naprave za shranjevanje, ko bo ta priključena ali priklopljena "
"na sistem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic mount"
msgstr "Samodejno namesti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This list contains the storage devices known to &plasma;. If <guilabel>On "
"Login</guilabel> is checked, the device will be automatically mounted even "
"though <guilabel>Automatically mount all removable media at login</guilabel> "
"is unchecked. The same applies for <guilabel>On Attach</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ta seznam vsebuje naprave za shranjevanje, ki jih pozna &plasma;. Če je "
"<guilabel>Ob prijavi</guilabel> označen,bo naprava samodejno nameščena, "
"čeprav ni označena možnost <guilabel>Samodejno namestiti vse izmenljive "
"medije ob prijavi</guilabel>. Enako velja za <guilabel>Ob pritrditvi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Enable automatic mounting of removable media</guilabel> is "
"unchecked, the overrides do not apply and no devices will be automatically "
"mounted."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje <guilabel>Omogoči samodejno nameščanje izmenljivih medijev</"
"guilabel> odkljukano, se prekriti parametri ne uporabljajo in nobena naprava "
"ne bo samodejno nameščena."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forget Device"
msgstr "Pozabi napravo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button causes &plasma; to <quote>forget</quote> that the "
"selected devices ever existed. This is only useful if <guilabel>Only "
"automatically mount removable media that has been manually mounted before</"
"guilabel> is checked. Once a device is forgotten and &plasma; is set to only "
"automatically mount familiar devices, the device will not be automatically "
"mounted."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta gumb &plasma; <quote>pozabi</quote>, da so izbrane naprave "
"sploh kdaj obstajale. To je uporabno le, če je označeno polje "
"<guilabel>Samodejno namesti izmenljive medije, ki so bili predhodno ročno "
"nameščeni</guilabel>. Ko je naprava pozabljena in je funkcija &plasma; "
"nastavljena na samodejno nameščanje samo znanih naprav, se naprava ne bo "
"samodejno namestila."
